cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with 3D scene completion and semantic segmentation, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of a generative 3D CNN model also suggests a potential connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the use of probabilistic models for semantic inference, which could also relate to natural language processing (cs.CL).
